{"tid":398930,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(內有極少劇透)(童傭兵+策略形男主)有冇巴打睇過「邊緣行動」","createTime":"2017-09-13T14:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T21:00:31.000Z","uid":6327,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"da8fa3f543a7839f3686eb1b1f85a5448c5952c8","tid":398930,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"故事係講廿幾歲既毒撚男主翻緊既公司倒閉 <br />\n之後搵左份工 而份工係負責好似打機咁玩d軍事策略模擬game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭幾集係講男主訓練打機同叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男主個職責就好似係戰場負責指引士兵同埋落order<br />\n好似軍火女王個koko咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭幾話都比較沉重同寫男主內心掙扎之類...因為男主同成班同事以為真係打機黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/214834_2944cf6fe40e1eb7fd3805ed20da3888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F214834_2944cf6fe40e1eb7fd3805ed20da3888.jpg&h=5a50f0c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/215409_c87e9b93e08b150805836691389c777c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F215409_c87e9b93e08b150805836691389c777c.jpg&h=69e81a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面👇呢個女主女同事 on9到震 個精靈耳係整形整 因為崇尚ACG文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/215628_44c3dec722cb207f1cbb7b90f8b0b326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F215628_44c3dec722cb207f1cbb7b90f8b0b326.jpg&h=7cc205c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到十零話開始入超級戲肉 一班童子兵<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">加百列真女主</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/220206_fa0348d5b7e3e3f7b9dca993666643f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F220206_fa0348d5b7e3e3f7b9dca993666643f1.jpg&h=5ddb83de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/220433_0b0765d7b3c73551a02a0e628c006780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F220433_0b0765d7b3c73551a02a0e628c006780.jpg&h=787def73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然沉重還沉重 但之後都幾多賣萌賣笑畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/221115_318941b609538c0324918028a4b80919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F221115_318941b609538c0324918028a4b80919.jpg&h=856d3d21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4974e49f4e81861577856d8b18b438093f6d09ec","tid":398930,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2011fce375c9aa53c53562a316ec1129dc65f2c1","tid":398930,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:35:18.000Z","msg":"知道精靈俾人女女女就冇睇落去"},{"pid":"c47cec10722e6048a6224a65c4242eab4243bb9b","tid":398930,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知道精靈俾人女女女就冇睇落去</blockquote><br />\n我睇到廿零話咋....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6dc988d17ca40adce484f06685ee9484bbc453","tid":398930,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"屌 原來係小說改編"},{"pid":"747127a6838998f582f2c8b9cd242575544d0b39","tid":398930,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\